{"tid":794122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有醫生憂全球暖化令登革熱成風土病","createTime":"2018-08-26T03:08:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-26T03:21:05.000Z","uid":13468,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"716375499dc5042080704ac051df0f3e860db5cc","tid":794122,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T03:08:24.000Z","msg":"有醫生憂全球暖化令登革熱成風土病<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】香港至今確診26宗本地感染登革熱個案，血液及血液腫瘤科醫生梁憲孫認為疫情仍屬早期爆發，但擔心登革熱會因氣候暖化而變風土病。<br />\n<br />\n血液及血液腫瘤科醫生梁憲孫：「一般來說病情不會很嚴重，大部分人都會自然康復，甚至有些人無病徵，感染了也不知道，目前來說不是很危險的情況，但始終有擔心隨着氣候暖化，香港的天氣比較熱、比較暖，香港會否將來好像新加坡、馬來西亞和印尼般成為風土病。落地生根。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=317993\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D317993&d=Ffc2IM8%2B%2BBCfU1b%2BtQePjozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=184ffd23\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D317993&h=ca26f40c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=317993</a>"},{"pid":"c77983bc1ec52d9480d20c55ec40b2da9a0c315f","tid":794122,"uid":153778,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T03:21:05.000Z","msg":"港樓依然gogogo<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}